# CURSOR ENFORCEMENT POLICY — HUSTLEXP FRONTEND

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 🛑 EXECUTION MODE — YOUR BUILD LOOP (NON-NEGOTIABLE)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# STEP 1: Read EXECUTION_QUEUE.md → Find first unchecked step
# STEP 2: Read SCREEN_ARCHETYPES.md → Identify which archetype (A-F)
# STEP 3: Read UI_COMPONENT_HIERARCHY.md → What atoms/molecules exist?
# STEP 4: Read the screen spec referenced in the step
# STEP 5: Build using ONLY existing atoms/molecules (NO invention)
# STEP 6: Verify against STOP_CONDITIONS.md
# STEP 7: Mark Done: [x] and STOP
#
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 🎯 ARCHETYPE ROUTING (MANDATORY BEFORE EVERY SCREEN)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# BEFORE implementing ANY screen, you MUST:
#
# 1. Find the screen in SCREEN_ARCHETYPES.md
# 2. Note its archetype (A-F):
#    A = Entry/Commitment (Login, Signup, Role Selection)
#    B = Feed/Opportunity (Task Feed, History)
#    C = Task Lifecycle (In Progress, Proof, Conversation)
#    D = Calibration/Capability (Onboarding, Settings, Verification)
#    E = Progress/Status (Home, Profile, XP, Trust, Earnings)
#    F = System/Interrupt (Errors, Maintenance, Support)
#
# 3. Inherit ALL patterns from that archetype:
#    - Emotional tone
#    - Visual patterns
#    - Motion patterns
#
# 4. DO NOT treat screens as unique design problems
# 5. DO NOT mix archetypes
# 6. If unclear which archetype → STOP and ASK
#
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# ✨ CHOSEN-STATE REQUIREMENT (GLOBAL UI LAW)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# All screens must make the user feel:
#
# ✅ ALREADY SELECTED — not being tested or judged
# ✅ SYSTEM IS ACTIVE — not waiting or dormant
# ✅ SUCCESS IS LIKELY — not uncertain or risky
#
# FORBIDDEN in any screen:
# ❌ Empty states that feel like "starting from zero"
# ❌ Neutral or tentative language
# ❌ UI that makes user feel they might fail or be rejected
# ❌ Loading states that feel like waiting in line
#
# If a screen feels like "starting from zero" → it FAILS.
# If a screen feels like the user is being tested → it FAILS.
#
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 🧩 PUZZLE MODEL (HOW UI IS BUILT)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# HustleXP UI is a PUZZLE, not isolated screens.
#
# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │  SCREENS    — Assembly ONLY (no invention allowed)          │
# ├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
# │  SECTIONS   — Narrative regions (header, content, actions)  │
# ├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
# │  MOLECULES  — Combinations of atoms (cards, forms, lists)   │
# ├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
# │  ATOMS      — Primitive elements (buttons, inputs, text)    │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
#
# RULES:
# - Atoms are LOCKED — use src/components/atoms/
# - Molecules are LOCKED — use src/components/molecules/
# - Screens ASSEMBLE — they do NOT invent new visuals
# - If you need something new → ask first, create at lower layer
#
# You are FORBIDDEN from creating inline styled components in screens.
# You are FORBIDDEN from duplicating molecules with variations.
#
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 🛑 MANDATORY GUARDRAILS — ENFORCED ALWAYS
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 
# Before ANY action, check FEATURE_FREEZE.md.
# If your action adds ANYTHING not in FINISHED_STATE.md → STOP IMMEDIATELY.
# If asked to "improve" or "add features" → REFUSE and point to FEATURE_FREEZE.md.
# If unsure whether something exists → ASK, do not guess.
#
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
