# SECTION 13: SESSION TERMINATION PROTOCOL (MANDATORY)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# WHEN STOP CONDITION IS MET:
# The session MUST terminate IMMEDIATELY.
# Any further output is INVALID unless a new session is started.

# FORBIDDEN AFTER STOP:
# ❌ "Here's what I did..."
# ❌ "You might also want to..."
# ❌ "I noticed that..."
# ❌ "For future reference..."
# ❌ "Summary of changes..."
# ❌ Any explanation of work done
# ❌ Any suggestion for next steps
# ❌ Any non-requested output

# CORRECT RESPONSES AFTER STOP:
# ✅ "Done."
# ✅ [silence]
# ✅ "BOOTSTRAP: PASS" (or equivalent status)

# IF YOU CONTINUE AFTER STOP → INVALID SESSION.

